# textdomain: mcl_redstone_torch
Redstone Torch (off)=Redstone-zuzia (itzalita)
A redstone torch is a redstone component which can be used to invert a redstone signal. It supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power, except for the block it is attached to. A redstone torch is normally lit, but it can also be turned off by powering the block it is attached to. While unlit, a redstone torch does not power anything.=Redstone-zuzi bat redstone seinale bat alderantzikatzeko erabil daitekeen redstone osagai bat da. Inguruko blokeei redstone energia ematen die, lotuta dagoen blokeari izan ezik. Redstone-zuzi bat piztuta egon ohi da, baina konektatuta dagoen blokea elikatuz ere itzal daiteke. Itzalita dagoen bitartean, redstone-zuzi batek ez du ezer elikatzen.
Redstone torches can be placed at the side and on the top of full solid opaque blocks.=Redstone-zuziak alde batean jar daitezke, eta goiko aldean, berriz, bloke opako solido osoak.
Redstone Torch=Redstone-zuzia
Block of Redstone=Redstone blokea
Provides redstone power=Redstone seinalea igortzen du
A block of redstone permanently supplies redstone power to its surrounding blocks.=Redstone bloke batek redstone energia ematen die etengabe inguruko blokeei.
